              <span id="reviewTextContainer2234881284" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer23459182025770637"><strong>Gripping story of faith, adventure and discovery</strong><br/><br/>This story is Jason Bourne meets Robert Langdon. The action of a unknowing faithless soldier crossed with the archaeological and historical search for answers about the true origins of religion and faith. Uncovering a lost crypt and learning lost secrets about the earliest figures in the Catholic Canon make for a great read. </span>

          </span>
