<span id="freeTextContainer100820739381451935"><strong>The pages kept flying!</strong><br/><br/>I chose this rating because it kept me awake long into the nights. I would try reading &quot;with one eye open&quot;, but would invariably wake up with the kindle on the floor and my glasses still on. This book is first rate thriller! I definitely want to read more by Stephen Marley. I recommend it to anyone who loves first-class mystery and some of the supernatural!</span>
